name: Traffic Racer Car speed Rally
description:
Enjoy a car racer game of the top free games.
Traffic Racer Car Speed Rally simulator is very interesting as fast speed car racing game.in this game you can drive a car in full speed and cross the others cars.also this car can jump and stunt from the top of others car.each level have a big challenge from the others level.when you will drive a car in full speed then you can cross the others car and will have great realistic stunt.amazing game with good control.
you will really enjoy this game.try it and play this game and feed back us
